plt.figure(figsize=(15,8))
ax1_x_axis_labels=['00:00','01:00','02:00','03:00','04:00','05:00','06:00','07:00','08:00','09:00','10:00','11:00','12:00',
                  '13:00','14:00','15:00','16:00','17:00','18:00','19:00','20:00','21:00','22:00','23:00']
ax1 = sns.histplot(x='hour', data=df_dcTotalCrimes,kde=True,hue='crimetype',stat='frequency',discrete=True,binrange=[0,23],multiple='stack')
ax1.set_xlabel('24-hour time')
ax1.set_ylabel('Frequency')
ax1.set_title('Frequency of Crimes Over a Day')
ax1.set_xticks(ticks=np.arange(0,24,1),labels=ax1_x_axis_labels)
ax1_legend = ax1.get_legend()
ax1_legend.set_title('Type of Crime')

total_crimes_by_hour = df_dcTotalCrimes[df_dcTotalCrimes['crimetype'] == 'Violent'].groupby('hour').count()['crimetype']

print("Hour with the highest crime is " + repr(total_crimes_by_hour.mode())[0] + " which has " + repr(total_crimes_by_hour.max()) + " crimes.")

Hour with the highest crime is 0 which has 4681 crimes.
